item.description: <p>The Alien Mothership has appeared in the city skyline to capture civilians. A brave reporter bears witness to it. The massive UFO spins above his head emitting eerie noises, and then releases its abducting claw to capture the reporter. With the LEGO Alien Conquest Alien Mothership, your child can save the reporter from the evil Alien Mothership so that he lives to tell his tale on the nightly news! The LEGO Alien Mothership set includes 416 pieces including minifigures, spinning outer disks and more. </p>

item.description: <p>The LEGO Space Shuttle thrills children with its wonderful theme of launching a rocket into deep space from the LEGO City. Your child has to help the astronaut open the cargo bay doors and release the Hubble Space Telescope into orbit using the robotic arm.<p> <p>The LEGO toy box contains 231 pieces and a minifigure of a spacesuit-wearing astronaut. The astronaut and the rocket together create a real space-like feel that will excite your little ones.  This adventure toy will enhance the imaginative skills of your children and sharpen their minds. The toy is aimed at children above five years of age. Your kids will enjoy learning about space travel with this LEGO 4598910 Space Shuttle.</p>

item.description: <p>The LEGO Mindstorms is back and is better than ever with new robot models and even more customizable LEGO building software programming and advanced technology. The LEGO Mindstorms NXT 2.0 Robogator combines the unlimited versatility of the Lego building system with an intelligent microcomputer brick and intuitive drag-and-drop programming software to give you the best robotic toy. </p><p>Create your first LEGO Mindstorm robot in just about 30 minutes and build many other robotic inventions that do what you want using this set. The kit includes 619 pieces and comes with instructions to build four robots. The color sensor present in this set differentiates between light settings and colors and also acts as a lamp. The combination of software, hardware, and quality NXT LEGO bricks will sure have you captivated and building robots for hours. If you are interested in robotics or want your kid to learn the basics of engineering, then this educational LEGO toy is a great choice.</p>

item.description: <p>Your child will have the time of his life saving the castle from the Dementors when he plays with the LEGO Harry Potter Hogwart's Castle building set. The LEGO building set includes a total of 1290 pieces. Your little one will love spending hours of fun putting up the Lego Hogwarts Castle. The Hogwarts castle is a place of magic and mystery. Explore the castle to discover your own personal favorite moments from the Harry Potter films. Develop your own stories and play with the Room of Requirement, Professor Lupin's office, the Astronomy Tower, the Divination Room and the Mirror of Erised. The toy set will be loved by all kid's who like by construction sets. It will also interest adults looking for a one-of-a-kind collector's item. The LEGO Hogwarts Castle set is a truly magical take on the world of LEGO bricks.</p>

item.description: With the LEGO City Police Station Play Set, your child must stop the prisoners from escaping the police station through the pipe drain. They won't get far on foot. Your little policeman can use the police car to chase them down and transport them back to prison in the police van. Lock criminals up in two jail cells, pull police vehicles into the garage, and even land a helicopter on the roof &mdash; kid's creative play has never been so detailed! Help keep LEGO City safe with this feature-packed LEGO City Police Station set that's packed with details &mdash; evidence room, mug shot area and secret compartment &mdash; that will keep kids wanting to construct, build, and play.

item.description: Set sail for the Fountain of Youth on the most dreaded ship on the high seas, the LEGO Pirates of the Caribbean Queen Anne's Revenge! Captain Jack Sparrow and his motley band of pirates are taking control of the Queen Anne's Revenge! It's mayhem and mutiny as they seize the ship from Angelica and her zombie crew. If they only knew that Blackbeard, the pirate all pirates fear, is watching and waiting in the LEGO Queen Anne set's captain's quarters. This time Jack has gone too far! From the captain's quarters perched high on his magnificent ship, Blackbeard secretly looks on as Captain Jack Sparrow and the motley crew attempt mutiny against Angelica and the zombies. Will our heroes be able to take control of the LEGO Pirates of the Caribbean Queen Anne's Revenge before Blackbeard reveals himself?

item.description: Visit Olivia's House with all of the LEGO Friends! Olivia, her parents and her pet cat live in a big, bright house with lots of rooms for hanging out and having fun. Help Olivia to grill up a barbeque for the girls. Mow the lawn with the lawnmower. Write in Olivia's diary and swing in the yard! Then, host a sleepover or have a party. Olivia's House is built in sections for easy rearranging. Decorate, customize and rebuild the LEGO Friends Olivia's House.

item.description: The LEGO Star Wars Millennium Falcon is the ultimate collection for both kids and adults who are Star Wars fans. You can now help Ben Kenobi in his quest against the dark side! This LEGO construction set is an amazing replica of Han Solo's starship. One of LEGO'S premium collection building sets, this LEGO Millennium Falcon set includes characters from Star Wars Falcon. The mini figurines and 1254 pieces allow for a variety of configurations. The LEGO Star Wars Millennium Falcon Toy is a perfect gift for the creative child (or adult) with interests in building blocks and space ships! Whether you're looking for something to occupy a kid's creative play time or a collectible piece of Star Wars memorabilia, this Millenium Falcon will provide hours of fun construction to children and adults alike.

item.description: With Lego Star Wars Luke's Landspeeder, you can build the vehicle that Luke Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi drive into the Tatooine spaceport of Mos Eisley. Recreate the epic moment when Obi-Wan first uses the Force on the Imperial sandtroopers by uttering "These are not the droids you're looking for." When he drove the old hermit Ben Kenobi into Mos Eisley spaceport, young farm boy Luke Skywalker had no idea that he would end up becoming a Jedi Knight and saving the galaxy. Recreate the moment the adventure began with this special-edition LEGO Star Wars Luke's Landspeeder set, featuring a landspeeder vehicle with a secret lightsaber compartment, a cast of droids and heroes, and a sandtrooper guard with a security droid. Are these the droids he's looking for?<br><p>Build up your Imperial forces and lead the attack on planet Hoth by launching flick-fire missiles from the battle station. Celebrate the 30th anniversary of The Empire Strikes Back movie with this terrific Lego 8084 Snow Troope

item.description: A replica of the real engine that operated on the railroads of America, the LEGO Creator Maersk Train features exceptional detailing and functions, such as opening driver's cab, removable side panel revealing a detailed, 16-cylinder engine, and authentic Maersk branding. The model also includes two wagons and three containers with opening doors (one with refrigeration detailing). The set also includes a shunter truck and detachable trailer for loading and offloading the containers.

item.description: Andrea works at the City Park Cafe and loves dishing out tasty treats, when she is not singing into her broom and daydreaming of her big performance. It's the perfect place in Heartlake City for all of the LEGO Friends to meet for milkshakes and burgers or to chill and have fun! You can bake goodies for the girls in the cafe kitchen, complete with everything you need to serve up cafe cuisine in style! Then hang in the outdoor dining area and have a milkshake in the sun! Order up a sweet snack, serve the customers and pay with LEGO money bricks!
